---
title: One-Pot Italian Beef & Risoni Stew with Parmesan
description: If you’re tossing up between having rice or pasta for dinner, may we offer you the perfect solution - risoni! Stir this risoni through beef and veggies in a saucy stew and it’s a guarantee everyone at the table will have smiles on their faces.
